'''osteoporosis''' (''plural'' '''osteoporoses''')

# {{pathology}} A [[disease]], occurring especially in [[women]] following [[menopause]], in which the [[bone]]s become [[extremely]] [[porous]] and are [[subject]] to [[fracture]].

